task.summary: Check before implementing Molle as a module in this intellij project.
Cross-testing with Molle has been implemented.

1. Bug that prevented the Molle parser to work correctly has now been fixed.
2. Tests to check correct functioning of the MolleAdapter have been successfully created.
3. Since we assume Molle gives a correct output, MolleAdapter has been successfully tested on giving the same output as Molle would, and my Theorem Prover has been successfully cross-tested on +100,000 formulas with the MolleAdapter, we can assume that my Theorem Prover now gives the correct output for the Modal Logic K.
